<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Friedrich IV. von Habsburg, Herzog von Österreich und Graf von Tirol</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Wilhelm Mendel, Ratsherr zu Nürnberg, wegen Beschlagnahmung vieler Waren Nürnberger Kaufleute im Gebiet des Adressaten an und bittet um gütliche Anhörung.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_99" id="48r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_99_r2l2"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>frıdrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hertʒog cʒu <expan>Oſt<ex>er</ex>reich</expan> / cʒu <expan>Stey<ex>er</ex></expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l3">cʒu kernden / vnd cʒu krain Graue cʒu Tyrol etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_99_r2l5">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / vns haben etliche vnſer <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> / vnd kaufleute fürbracht / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l6">vvie daʒ Jn etvvieuil habe / vnd kaufmanſchafte in <expan>ewre<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan> / herſchaft / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l7">gepieten bekümert ſeÿ woꝛden / darümb ſo ſenden vvir cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> durchleuhtıkeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l8">vnſern <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Ratgeſell<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>VVilhel<ex>m</ex></expan> Mendell / VVeiſer ditʒ briefs / mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l9"><expan>fürſtenlıch<ex>en</ex></expan> gnaden dauon cʒereden / vnd <expan>Rogam<ex>us</ex></expan> / vvas derſelbe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_line_1574763348090_308"><expan>Ratgeſell<ex>e</ex></expan> darümb cʒu diſem mal / an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>hochwirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan> werbe / von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l12">daʒ Jn <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>durchlüh<ex>tikeit</ex></expan> darÿnne <expan>gnedıglıch<ex>en</ex></expan> verhöꝛen / vnd Jm des glauben / vnd Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l13">auch <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> gneͣdiglichen auſʒrichten / vnd von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vertigen wölle / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_line_1574764006002_348">Als etc das <expan>woll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> feria iiij̃ ante Bartholomei Anno etc Octauo $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_99" id="48r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, herczog czu
                            <expan>Ost<ex>er</ex>reich</expan>, czu <expan>Stey<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                        czu Kernden und czu Krain, grave czu Tyrol etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns haben etliche unser
                                <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kaufleute fürbracht, wie daz in
                        etwievil habe und kaufmanschafte in <expan>ewre<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan>, herschaft und gepieten bekümert sey worden.
                        Darümb so senden wir czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> durchleuhtikeit unsern
                                <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und <expan>ratgesell<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>Wilhel<ex>m</ex></expan> Mendell, weiser dicz briefs, mit
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>en</ex></expan> gnaden davon czereden. Und
                                <expan>rogam<ex>us</ex></expan>, was derselbe
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex></expan> darümb
                        czu disem mal an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hochwirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan> werbe von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>durchlüh<ex>tikeit</ex></expan> darynne
                            <expan>gnediglich<ex>en</ex></expan> verhören und im des glauben und in
                        auch <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> gneͣdiglichen auszrichten und von
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vertigen wölle, als etc. Das
                                <expan>woll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        feria iiii ante Bartholomei anno etc. octavo.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
